%% Diagram: Dedup window vs retry timeout (SQS FIFO 5 min example)
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant Broker as Broker (5 min dedup window)
    participant Consumer

    Note over Client,Consumer: t = 0 — first send
    Client->>Broker: send(msg, id=X)
    Broker->>Broker: remember id=X (window starts)
    Broker->>Consumer: deliver msg
    Consumer-->>Broker: ack lost on the wire

    Note over Client: Retry policy: backoff up to 10 min
    Note over Broker: t = 5:01 — Broker forgets id=X

    Note over Client,Consumer: t = 6:00 — client retries
    Client->>Broker: send(msg, id=X)
    Broker->>Broker: id=X is now "new"
    Broker->>Consumer: deliver msg again
    Note right of Consumer: Duplicate processing despite\n"exactly-once" guarantee
